What you need to know:

Chris Ochieng and Chrispinus Onyango scored a goal apiece as the brewers got the better of Leopards, who have beaten them twice this season.Ochieng and Onyango took full advantage of their inclusion in the starting line-up in place of Henry Meja and Boniface Muchiri who are away with the national team for the Cecafa Challenge Cup to stab home the goals.